                                                         BUSINESS QUESTION
What factors drive higher lifetime value?

                     QUERY
SELECT
CASE WHEN discount_usage_rate > 20 THEN 'HIGH DISCOUNT'
ELSE 'low discount'
END AS DISCOUNT_LEVELS, 
ROUND(AVG(lifetime_value),2)Total_revenue
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY DISCOUNT_LEVELS;

INSIGHT;
Customers who use higher discounts tend to have higher purchases and lifetime value, but this does not fully mean discounts alone are driving the revenue.

Recommendation (fixed)
Instead of always giving discounts, we can use them strategically during certain periods and combine them with other incentives to maintain profit.
